<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Natural Healing</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">1 per level</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Increases the speed at which the player recovers hitpoints. Each level increases the heal rate by 1 per tick. Stacks with all other forms of HP regen including Innate Regeneration.</P>
											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Combat Fury</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">2%/4%/7%</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Increases the chance to land a critical strike (“melee crit”) on an opponent. “Non-warriors will nearly match the original critical hit abilities of Warriors, while Warriors will remain significantly ahead of other classes.”</P>
											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Fear Resistance</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">5%/10%/25%</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Increases the player’s chance to resist being feared, including Dragon Fear. Also increases the chance to break fear sooner. 1st level increases resistance by 5%, 2nd by 10%, and 3rd by 25%.</P>
											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Finishing Blow</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">NPCs below lvl 50/52/54</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Adds a chance to kill an NPC that is below 10% health and fleeing with a single blow. (Monsters that do not flee are not affected by this ability.) Prerequisite: Combat Fury</P>
											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Combat Stability</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">2%/5%/10%</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
