											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Combat Agility</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">2%/5%/10%</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Increases the player’s ability to avoid being hit altogether. 1st level increases the chances to avoid a blow by 2%, 2nd level by 5%, 3rd level by 10%.</P>
											</TD>
										</TR>
<TR>
											<TD width="21">
												<P align="center">55</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="81">
												<P align="center">Mental Clarity</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="48">
												<P align="center">2/4/6</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="45">
												<P align="center">3</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="96">
												<P align="center">1 mana/tick per AA level</P>
											</TD>
											<TD width="429">
												<P>Increases the player’s base mana regeneration rate. Each level increases the mana regained by 1 point per tick. Stacks with all other forms of mana regeneration.</P>
											</TD>
